    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n6887" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὁράω, ὁρόω</span></b>  (root <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ϝορ</span>), ipf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὅρᾱ,
            ὁρῶμεν</span>, mil. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὁρῶμαι</span>, 2
          sing. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὅρηαι</span>, ipf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὁρᾶτο, ὁρῶντο</span> (from root <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὀπ</span>, perf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὄπωπα</span>, plup. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὀπώπει</span>, mid.
          fut. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὄψεαι, ὄψει</span>, 2 pl. [or aor. imp.]
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὄψεσθε</span>; from root <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ϝιδ</span>, see <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">εἴδω</span>
          I.): act. and mid., <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">see, behold, look on;</span> freq.
          phrases, (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐν</span>) <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὀφθαλμοῖσιν ὁρᾶν, ὁρᾶσθαι, ὁρᾶν φαος ἠελίοιο</span> (= <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ζῆν</span>).</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
